channel.title: Help with Port Forwarding
channel.description:
I have port forwarded many times before. But this time I am getting problems. For anyone's information I have a Linksys WRT110 Router. I have everything entered correctly. But when I go to check the ports or log into my server. It is not online nor are the ports open. If I could please get some assistance. I've been going at it all day and to be honest. It is frustrating me to the max. Sorry to ask for such help. But if you could I would much appreciate it. Thank you.
PS. If we need to go on teamviewer. I am willing.
